<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Web Pro — ESP Dakar</title>
    <style>
        :root { --accent: #4ade80; --bg: #111; --card: #1a1a1a; }
        body { background: var(--bg); color: #ccc; font-family: 'Segoe UI', monospace; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
        
        header { background: #000; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; }
        nav { display: flex; sticky; top: 0; background: #161616; overflow-x: auto; }
        nav button { flex: 1; padding: 15px; background: none; border: none; color: #666; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; }
        nav button.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        .tab-content { display: none; }
        .tab-content.active { display: block; }

        .card { background: var(--card); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        pre { background: #000; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; color: #4ade80; font-size: 13px; }
        
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0; }
        th, td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; text-align: left; }
        th { color: var(--accent); }

        .quiz-item { background: #181818; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .btn-opt { background: #222; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; margin: 5px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 4px; }
        .btn-opt:hover { background: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1 style="margin:0; color:#fff;">Web Dev — ESP</h1>
    <small style="color:var(--accent)">Dr. M. DIOP | Licence SRT</small>
</header>

<nav>
    <button class="active" onclick="show('html')">HTML</button>
    <button onclick="show('css')">CSS</button>
    <button onclick="show('js')">JS</button>
    <button onclick="show('quiz')">QUIZ</button>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <section id="html" class="tab-content active">
        <h2>Structure & Contenu</h2>
        <p>Le HTML définit <strong>quoi</strong> afficher. Chaque page suit ce squelette :</p>
        <pre>&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt; &lt;title&gt;Ma Page&lt;/title&gt; &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Titre&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Texte &lt;a href="#"&gt;Lien&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;img src="pic.jpg" alt="Description" /&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</pre>
        <div class="card">
            <strong>Balises clés :</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> à <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> : Titres</li>
                <li><code>&lt;ul&gt; / &lt;ol&gt;</code> : Listes</li>
                <li><code>&lt;table&gt;</code> : Tableaux</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="css" class="tab-content">
        <h2>Style & Design</h2>
        <p>Le CSS définit <strong>comment</strong> afficher (couleurs, tailles, positions).</p>
        <pre>selector { property: value; }

/* Exemple */
h1 { color: blue; text-align: center; }
.maClasse { background: yellow; }
#monId { font-weight: bold; }</pre>
        <div class="card">
            <strong>Où l'écrire ?</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>Fichier externe : <code>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" ...&gt;</code></li>
                <li>En-tête : <code>&lt;style&gt;</code></li>
                <li>En ligne : <code>style="..."</code></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="js" class="tab-content">
        <h2>Interactivité (JS)</h2>
        <p>JavaScript anime la page et gère les données.</p>
        <pre>let x = prompt("Ton nom ?");
alert("Bonjour " + x);

function calculer(a) {
    return a * 2;
}

// Evènement
document.getElementById('btn').onclick = function() { ... };</pre>
        <div class="card">
            <strong>Objets du Navigateur :</strong>
            <code>window</code> (fenêtre), <code>document</code> (contenu), <code>location</code> (URL).
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="quiz" class="tab-content">
        <h2>Test Rapide</h2>
        <div class="quiz-item">
            <p>1. Le HTML est un langage de programmation ?</p>
            <button class="btn-opt" onclick="check(this, false)">Vrai</button>
            <button class="btn-opt" onclick="check(this, true)">Faux (Description)</button>
        </div>
        <div class="quiz-item">
            <p>2. Quel sélecteur cible un ID ?</p>
            <button class="btn-opt" onclick="check(this, false)">.point</button>
            <button class="btn-opt" onclick="check(this, true)">#dièse</button>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<script>
    function show(id) {
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
        document.querySelectorAll('nav button').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
        document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
        event.currentTarget.classList.add('active');
    }

    function check(btn, isCorrect) {
        btn.style.background = isCorrect ? "#1a3a1a" : "#3a1a1a";
        btn.style.color = isCorrect ? "#4ade80" : "#ff4444";
        btn.style.borderColor = isCorrect ? "#4ade80" : "#ff4444";
        alert(isCorrect ? "Bravo !" : "Réessaie...");
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
